			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="4" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="| In SCL - TOWN - Masonry there is a pile of crashed bones on display. The plaque nearby suggests these are the bones of the head Mason who had conspiracy agains Sharrans. &#xD;&#xA;Player can spot here that something is off with these bones - like the skeletons contains bones of different people |" />
